data.description: This property is perfect for those seeking a cozy and comfortable home in a convenient location. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the fresh interior paint and updated light fixtures and open layout that enhance the overall ambiance of the house. One of the highlights of this property is its outdoor space. Imagine enjoying cool evenings by the outdoor fire pit, creating lasting memories with loved ones. The yard is level, and the privacy fence ensures a sense of seclusion and tranquility.During colder months, cozy up by the fireplace in the living room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The main bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet, providing ample storage space.Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers convenience at your fingertips. Just minutes from Downtown Hollister, Branson Landing & Hollister Schools.
